### Aurelia API — Phase 4 inspections collection
### VS Code REST Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@inspectionTypeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@templateId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@inspectionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
@checklistItemId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
@findingId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005
@followupId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006
@evidenceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007

### List inspection types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/types

### List checklist templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/templates

### Dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/dashboard/summary

### Create inspection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inspectionTypeId": "{{inspectionTypeId}}",
  "templateId": "{{templateId}}",
  "title": "Inspeccion de prueba",
  "description": "Registro MVP para validar Fase 4",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-06-24T14:00:00.000Z",
  "latitude": -33.4489,
  "longitude": -70.6693,
  "notes": "Creada desde REST Client"
}

### List inspections
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections

### List inspections by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections?status=draft

### Get inspection detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}

### Update inspection
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "startedAt": "2026-06-24T14:10:00.000Z",
  "reason": "Inicio de ejecucion"
}

### Update inspection status only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "submitted",
  "comment": "Inspeccion enviada a revision"
}

### Upsert checklist answer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checklistItemId": "{{checklistItemId}}",
  "answerValue": "compliant",
  "answerText": "Respuesta de prueba",
  "answeredAt": "2026-06-24T14:20:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Respuesta registrada desde REST Client"
}

### List findings for inspection
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/findings

### Create finding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/findings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checklistItemId": "{{checklistItemId}}",
  "title": "Residuo fuera de lugar",
  "description": "Se observa residuo fuera del punto definido",
  "severity": "medium",
  "dueAt": "2026-06-30T18:00:00.000Z"
}

### Update finding
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/findings/{{findingId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed",
  "reason": "Accion correctiva verificada"
}

### Create followup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/findings/{{findingId}}/followups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "description": "Se retira residuo y se verifica orden del area",
  "performedAt": "2026-06-25T15:00:00.000Z"
}

### Update followup
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/followups/{{followupId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "description": "Seguimiento actualizado desde REST Client"
}

### Close inspection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Todos los hallazgos fueron cerrados"
}

### List inspection evidences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/evidences

### Link existing evidence to inspection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "relationType": "inspection_evidence"
}

### List inspection comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/comments

### Create inspection comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Comentario de prueba asociado a la inspeccion",
  "isInternal": false
}

### Export inspection payload
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inspections/{{inspectionId}}/export
